&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NEW-YORK-NO-8-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8349&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NEW-YORK-NO-8-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;NEW YORK- NO 8- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;In New York&rsquo;s Chelsea art district, No. 8 is one of New York&rsquo;s most famously discreet lounges in the former location of Bungalow 8. Guests will find a selection of small plates, flowing cocktails and bottle service, including creative mixers such as fresh watermelon juice. The d&eacute;cor is elegant, the crowd is beautiful and the music will keep you moving. Strict door policy. Chic attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Grace Fernandez at Rec Room by email at grace@no8ny.com to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access n to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8 requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation for table or bottle service. A credit card authorization form will be sent at the time of booking to be filled in and returned back.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled or no-show 48 hours prior to the scheduled date a 20% fee to the agreed minimum stated at the time of booking will be charged to the credit card on file.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the nightclub by phone or email 24 hours prior to your arrival date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access reservation and advise if it&rsquo;s a special occasion. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chic attire is a must. Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserve seating is ONLY with bottle service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

